Welcome to TestiFi - a tool to help you put your story into words

We’re here to help you share your story with ease. No need to worry about perfect words, just share your thoughts one step at a time, and we’ll help you craft it into a message you can confidently share.

This tool is still in development, so there may be a few bumps along the way. Your feedback will help us improve, and rest assured, your story will remain confedential.

Let's start by talking about how you met Jesus. What was your life like before you found Christ?
